  • removeLayoutItem(layoutInfo: LayoutInfo, removeContent: boolean, removeAllSizeModeContent?: boolean): this
    • Defined in jimu-for-builder/lib/app-config-actions.ts:381

    Parameters

    • layoutInfo: LayoutInfo
